/a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Phi%E1%BA%BFm-Th%C3%A1i-H%E1%BB%93-th%C6%B0-s%E1%BB%B1-k%C3%BD-Vi-Chi/poem-BzLZ1rCYG7pM5QOEU16yKw">Phiếm Thái Hồ thư sự, ký Vi Chi - 泛太湖書事，寄微之</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-Qu%C3%A1ch-c%E1%BA%A5p-s%E1%BB%B1-Thang-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-linh-t%C6%B0u-t%C3%A1c/poem-ZFALwW-Oh0NxiQJY2bUNPQ">Phụng đồng Quách cấp sự “Thang đông linh tưu tác” - 奉同郭給事湯東靈湫作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng/T%E1%BB%87-l%C6%B0/poem-zF5F2fuJpi-tBv6pkHM98A">Tệ lư - 斃驢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng/author-PuXksgdBieGiSiRcb1zBAQ">Lý Động</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Th%E1%BB%AD-kh%E1%BB%91n-h%C3%AD-ngo%E1%BA%A1-h%C3%A0-di%E1%BB%87p-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-Phan-sinh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-RReN8sm3vA3OIUGrZbmgIw">Thử khốn hí ngoạ hà diệp thượng đồng Phan sinh kỳ 1 - 暑困戲臥荷葉上同潘生其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
